### Add a Review
POST http://localhost:3000/reviews
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <your-auth-token>

{
  "productId": "64b1cfd6f46eaf001c2bdb71",
  "userId": "64b1cfd6f46eaf001c2bdb70",
  "rating": 5,
  "comment": "Amazing product!"
}

###

### Fetch Reviews for a Product
GET http://localhost:3000/reviews/64b1cfd6f46eaf001c2bdb71
Authorization: Bearer <your-auth-token>

###

### Update a Review
PUT http://localhost:3000/reviews/64b1cfd6f46eaf001c2bdb72
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <your-auth-token>

{
  "userId": "64b1cfd6f46eaf001c2bdb70",
  "rating": 4,
  "comment": "Updated review: Still great, but shipping was slow."
}

###

### Delete a Review (Admin only)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/reviews/64b1cfd6f46eaf001c2bdb72
Authorization: Bearer <your-admin-auth-token>
